## 📥 Data Source

The dataset utilized for this analysis contains over 7,000 operational transaction records. 
To comply with GitHub file size limitations and maintain a clean repository, the raw data file is hosted externally.

* **Dataset Source:** [Kaggle - Bike Sales Dataset in Europe]
(https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/dillonmyrick/bike-store-sample-database)
* **Dataset Format:** Single Flat CSV File

### 📊 Database Volume & Row Count Breakdown

