| **Production**    | `categories` | Core product classifications              | 7 rows         |
| **Production**    | `brands`     | Bike manufacturer names                   | 9 rows         |
| **Production**    | `products`   | Complete bicycle item catalog             | 321 rows       |
| **Production**    | `stocks`     | Live inventory ledger per physical branch | 939 rows       |
| **Sales**         | `stores`     | Physical retail store locations           | 3 rows         |
| **Sales**         | `staffs`     | Employee records and team hierarchies     | 10 rows        |
| **Sales**         | `customers`  | Client demographic details                | 1,445 rows     |
| **Sales**         | `orders`     | Central transaction headers               | 1,615 rows     |
